  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BodyWithSynapses
    A class representing a body that contains synapses, as read from a synapses JSON file.
    BodyWithSynapsesTest
    Tests the BodyWithSynapses class.
    ConnectionSet
    A class representing a ConnectionSet node, which contains the Synapse nodes connecting a presynaptic body to a postsynaptic body.
    ConnectionSetMap
    A class representing a map of all ConnectionSet nodes for a given dataset.
    ConnectionSetMapTest
    Tests the ConnectionSetMap class.
    ConnectionSetTest
    Tests the ConnectionSet class.
    MetaInfo  
    Neuron
    A class representing a neuron, as read from a neuron JSON file.
    NeuronTest
    Tests the Neuron class.
    RoiInfo

    RoiInfoTest
    Tests the RoiInfo class.
    Skeleton
    A class representing a skeleton read from an swc file.
    SkeletonTest
    Tests the Skeleton class.
    SkelNode
    A class representing a spherical node of a Skeleton read from an swc file.
    SkelNodeTest
    Tests the SkelNode class.
    Soma
    A class representing a neuron's soma.
    SortBodyByNumberOfSynapses
    A class for sorting BodyWithSynapses objects by the number of synapses they possess in descending order.
    Synapse
    A class representing a synaptic density.
    SynapseCounter
    A class for counting the number of presynaptic and postsynaptic densities on a neuron.
    SynapseCounterTest
    Tests the SynapseCounter class.
    SynapseLocationToBodyIdMap

    Tests the Synapse class.
